Former BBNaija Season 5 ‘Lockdown’ housemate, Tochukwu Okechukwu aka Tochi has hit a lady who posed for a photo with the Labour Party presidential candidate, Peter Obi. A viral photo recently surfaced of a lady who stood for a photograph with the former Anambra Governor. The lady excitedly stood beside Obi with her right hand placed on his shoulder, almost as if she were leaning on him while the politician simply let out a smile. Read Also ; Why infidelity of Lagos girls hurts more – Tochi But the nightlife influencer queried the lady for placing her hand on Obi’s shoulder, describing her as disrespectful. He tweeted: “Why will you put your hand on his shoulder like that!!! Very disrespectful.”